nt-size: 18px;">经管新生爆照第一弹～</span></p><p style="line-height: 1.75em; text-align: center;"><span style="letter-spacing: 1.5px; line-height: 2.07em; font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; font-size: 18px;">新生报道现场</span></p><p style="text-align: center;"><img src="http://localhost:20829/upload/img/imgQuality_1/20240905/1725531480142060267.png" title="1725531480142060267.png" alt="63c86123a9d8722c209495977d8f826.png"/></p><p style="text-align: center;"><img src="http://localhost:20829/upload/img/imgQuality_1/20240905/1725531495723069696.png" title="1725531495723069696.png" alt="84c9cf62099761e85d72079fedcb147.png"/></p><p style="text-align: center;"><img src="http://localhost:20829/upload/img/imgQuality_1/20240905/1725531535917037720.png" title="1725531535917037720.png" alt="37d59731cfd5d15b4dc1cc148736c15.png"/></p><p style="text-align: center;"><span style="font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; font-size: 18px;">合影留念</span></p><p style="text-align: center;"><img src="http://localhost:20829/upload/img/imgQuality_1/20240905/1725531589578066237.png" title="1725531589578066237.png" alt="8f2f8bc7afad355aa59d877a65c13ed.png"/></p><p style="text-align: center;"><img src="http://localhost:20829/upload/img/imgQuality_1/20240905/1725531597979005363.png" title="1725531597979005363.png" alt="61aba67807340d69dc26807ad3bca92.png"/></p><p style="text-align: center;"><span style="font-size: 18px; font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;;">今天的迎新工作暂时告一段落</span></p><p style="text-align: center;"><span style="font-size: 18px; font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;;">这些充满朝气与活力的新面孔</span></p><p style="text-align: center;"><span style="font-size: 18px; font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;;">即将在大学校园里</span></p><p style="text-align: center;"><span style="font-size: 18px; font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;;">开启属于他们的精彩篇章</span></p><p style="text-align: center;"><span style="font-size: 18px; font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;;">让我